00:56:31,119 --> 00:56:33,330
In endless wake, moments stretch

519
00:56:33,538 --> 00:56:35,248
Twisting, turning, tossing, thinking

520
00:56:35,457 --> 00:56:38,293
Thinking, thinking of you

521
00:56:48,470 --> 00:56:51,014
Her images criss-cross my mind,

522
00:56:51,222 --> 00:56:53,183
awash in colours

523
00:56:53,391 --> 00:56:56,144
Like a gushing stream she flows,

524
00:56:56,353 --> 00:57:01,941
drenching me

525
00:57:03,443 --> 00:57:07,030
Her murmurs make music

526
00:57:08,323 --> 00:57:11,993
Her trivia are priceless

527
00:57:13,161 --> 00:57:15,622
Some innocence,
sweet mischief

528
00:57:15,830 --> 00:57:17,832
Somewhat gossamer,
some odd gloss

529
00:57:18,041 --> 00:57:20,543
At times bashful, then carefree

530
00:57:20,752 --> 00:57:23,588
There are seas in her, but how deep?

531
00:58:18,601 --> 00:58:23,565
Her words could make
Spring blossom

532
00:58:26,067 --> 00:58:31,114
Her charm could make
seasons spring

533
00:58:33,491 --> 00:58:35,368
Even her lies...

534
00:58:35,577 --> 00:58:36,619
are so endearing,

535
00:58:36,828 --> 00:58:40,206
she could make me believe
illusions in all things

536
00:58:41,207 --> 00:58:46,171
Upon her many paths,
praying, hoping, eager-eyed,

537
00:58:46,379 --> 00:58:51,092
musing fragrant shades of memories,
I stand still and...

538
00:58:51,301 --> 00:58:53,094
Time stands stilled

539
00:59:25,835 --> 00:59:35,804
BIGPictures

540
01:00:05,041 --> 01:00:07,627
Good morning, sir!
- Good morning.

541
01:00:07,836 --> 01:00:12,716
Sit down, my child. Guess what,
our company is going to be famous.

542
01:00:12,841 --> 01:00:14,467
Thanks only to you...
- Why are you thanking me?

543
01:00:14,676 --> 01:00:17,637
I've done something
without asking you.

544
01:00:18,555 --> 01:00:23,643
Our company is throwing a
big party on New Year's Eve.

545
01:00:23,852 --> 01:00:24,936
Oh, wow!

546
01:00:25,353 --> 01:00:26,980
Guess, who's the chief guest?

547
01:00:27,188 --> 01:00:27,856
Who...?

548
01:00:28,064 --> 01:00:29,774
Your boyfriend.

549
01:00:30,025 --> 01:00:31,860
The man who owns Air Voice.

550
01:00:32,068 --> 01:00:35,572
Sanjay Singhania.

551
01:00:35,905 --> 01:00:36,489
Sir...?

552
01:00:37,032 --> 01:00:40,869
And come what may,
you must get him to come.

553
01:00:41,536 --> 01:00:45,957
I'm sure you can, so I went ahead and
printed his name in the invitations.

554
01:00:46,875 --> 01:00:51,838
The biggest of agencies are coming,
top ad film makers, producers, directors.

555
01:00:52,380 --> 01:00:55,508
On whose say-so have
you printed his name?

556
01:00:55,717 --> 01:00:57,302
Where's the need to ask...?

557
01:00:58,762 --> 01:01:01,431
It's the New Years Eve party.
You're coming.

558
01:01:01,639 --> 01:01:05,060
He'll accompany you.
- But I can't invite him!

559
01:01:05,727 --> 01:01:06,186
Why?

560
01:01:07,729 --> 01:01:09,856
We've... had a fight!

561
01:01:11,066 --> 01:01:13,610
You don't say!
All invitations have been distributed.

562
01:01:13,818 --> 01:01:16,363
You've got to make up with him
...got to get him to the party.

563
01:01:16,613 --> 01:01:18,239
But how...?
- Otherwise, I'll lose face.

564
01:01:18,406 --> 01:01:21,326
On whose say-so did you print this?

565
01:01:21,618 --> 01:01:25,246
I would've told you,
but it slipped my mind.

566
01:01:25,455 --> 01:01:28,249
What you've done is so wrong,
hundred percent wrong!

567
01:01:28,458 --> 01:01:32,545
Please, or you'll break everyone's heart.
- Where will I get Sanjay Singhania?

568
01:01:32,754 --> 01:01:36,174
Everyone's dying to see him,
not one of us has ever met him.

569
01:01:38,635 --> 01:01:39,219
What...?

570
01:01:40,178 --> 01:01:41,388
What about what?

571
01:01:42,263 --> 01:01:44,933
Not one of us has ever met him?

572
01:01:45,183 --> 01:01:47,602
How could we?
He has just returned from America.

573
01:01:48,436 --> 01:01:49,980
Then I just...
must get him.

574
01:01:50,605 --> 01:01:52,607
Consider it done

575
01:01:52,857 --> 01:01:57,070
Kalpana is like a magic wand!
One flourish and you've got your wish.

576
01:01:57,821 --> 01:01:59,489
Thank you very much

577
01:02:04,995 --> 01:02:06,788
Dialogue... dialogue!

578
01:02:07,247 --> 01:02:10,959
Hi, I'm Sanjay. Sanjay Singhania.

579
01:02:11,167 --> 01:02:12,210
Perfect.

580
01:02:13,003 --> 01:02:13,920
Very good.

581
01:02:14,796 --> 01:02:15,672
Mind it.

582
01:02:15,880 --> 01:02:19,092
At tonight's party,
you're Sanjay Singhania.

583
01:02:20,969 --> 01:02:21,761
One second...

584
01:02:27,309 --> 01:02:31,354
Listen, that's a friend of mine.
You'll pretend to be Sanjay Singhania.

585
01:02:31,646 --> 01:02:34,524
If he's convinced,
then you pass muster. Okay?

586
01:02:37,068 --> 01:02:37,861
Ready?

587
01:02:40,196 --> 01:02:40,780
Hi...

588
01:02:40,989 --> 01:02:42,741
Hush!

589
01:02:43,158 --> 01:02:43,783
What happened?

590
01:02:44,826 --> 01:02:45,785
Sanjay is here.

591
01:02:45,994 --> 01:02:46,703
Sanjay?

592
01:02:47,495 --> 01:02:49,497
Sanjay Singhania, my boyfriend.

593
01:03:03,845 --> 01:03:06,014
Where... is he?
- Where are you looking...?

594
01:03:06,848 --> 01:03:07,349
Here!

595
01:03:08,683 --> 01:03:09,434
Sachin,

596
01:03:09,726 --> 01:03:10,977
meet Mr Sanjay.

597
01:03:11,853 --> 01:03:15,023
Hi, I'm Sanjay. Sanjay Singhania.

598
01:03:15,565 --> 01:03:16,650
What... who...?

599
01:03:18,860 --> 01:03:21,154
He is... Sanjay Singhania.

600
01:03:21,363 --> 01:03:22,030
Him...?

601
01:03:25,367 --> 01:03:28,036
Are you joking?
Sanjay Singhania, and him?

602
01:03:43,551 --> 01:03:46,262
Stupid amateur, duffer, idiot!

603
01:03:46,471 --> 01:03:48,264
What did I do...?

604
01:03:48,473 --> 01:03:52,811
The big fish never put out their hands first.
Why did you hold out your hand?

605
01:03:53,311 --> 01:03:56,940
So when do I shake hands?
- You just don't do it!

606
01:03:57,148 --> 01:03:59,651
Go to hell, go do ads!
You've ruined it all.

607
01:04:01,653 --> 01:04:02,320
Idiot!

608
01:04:05,573 --> 01:04:06,366
What happened?

609
01:04:06,950 --> 01:04:10,495
Sachin, shall I tell you something?

610
01:04:10,704 --> 01:04:11,287
What?

611
01:04:11,496 --> 01:04:13,498
You're going to be stunned...

612
01:04:13,957 --> 01:04:14,624
Try me.

613
01:04:14,833 --> 01:04:17,627
I'm not in love with Sanjay Singhania.

614
01:04:18,169 --> 01:04:18,670
What?

615
01:04:21,589 --> 01:04:22,841
Actually,

616
01:04:23,800 --> 01:04:25,593
everyone at my workplace thought...

617
01:04:25,802 --> 01:04:27,178
he's my boyfriend.

618
01:04:28,388 --> 01:04:30,348
So, everyone began to respect me.

619
01:04:33,059 --> 01:04:34,769
I played along.

620
01:04:36,604 --> 01:04:39,607
I don't even know what he looks like!

621
01:04:41,735 --> 01:04:43,903
So... what's next?

622
01:04:44,612 --> 01:04:46,573
My boss is hosting a party tonight.

623
01:04:46,781 --> 01:04:50,285
Without even asking me, they sent out
invites naming Sanjay as the chief guest.

624
01:04:50,493 --> 01:04:55,081
So I was preparing this mule for tonight,
but you caught him out in a second!

625
01:04:56,082 --> 01:04:58,084
What am I going to do now?

626
01:04:59,544 --> 01:05:01,838
Relax... I'm right here for you.

627
01:05:02,339 --> 01:05:03,923
I'll train him.

628
01:05:05,258 --> 01:05:06,801
Listen... what's your name?

629
01:05:07,427 --> 01:05:12,766
Hi, I'm Sanjay. Sanjay Singhania.
- No... your real name?

630
01:05:13,183 --> 01:05:14,809
Sampat.
- Look Sampat...

631
01:05:15,644 --> 01:05:17,228
cut that extra swagger.

632
01:05:17,437 --> 01:05:19,689
Be relaxed and easy... confident.

633
01:05:20,273 --> 01:05:22,984
Let me show how...
Hi, I'm Sanjay... Sanjay Singhania.

634
01:05:23,193 --> 01:05:28,448
Stop. Don't teach me acting.
I belong in theatre, I've done four plays.

635
01:05:28,657 --> 01:05:31,618
I was putting out a first class act,
then he walked in and things went awry.

636
01:05:31,826 --> 01:05:33,495
Hey... take off that coat.

637
01:05:34,496 --> 01:05:37,999
Take it off, get out of that coat!
- I have a shoot tomorrow. It's my only coat.

638
01:05:38,208 --> 01:05:41,961
I just canceled your shoot. You're good only
for rubber slippers, snap out of it!

639
01:05:44,839 --> 01:05:45,674
Who, me...?
- Wear it.

640
01:05:54,307 --> 01:05:57,227
Oh yes!
You are... looking smart.

641
01:05:58,561 --> 01:05:59,521
Put on the goggles.

642
01:06:04,150 --> 01:06:06,069
Oh wow!

643
01:06:06,861 --> 01:06:07,821
Perfect!

644
01:06:09,489 --> 01:06:10,365
Perfect!

645
01:06:11,533 --> 01:06:15,328
Sachin! Come for tonight's party.
Be Sanjay.

646
01:06:16,204 --> 01:06:17,288
Please?

647
01:06:17,831 --> 01:06:19,290
Please say yes!

648
01:06:20,083 --> 01:06:20,917
Please!

649
01:06:22,627 --> 01:06:23,545
Please say yes...?

650
01:06:24,546 --> 01:06:25,005
Okay.

651
01:06:25,505 --> 01:06:25,964
Yes!

652
01:06:26,172 --> 01:06:28,883
Welcome to our chief guest,
Mr Sanjay Singhania

653
01:06:36,558 --> 01:06:37,559
Oh hi...
- Hello.

654
01:06:39,269 --> 01:06:41,271
Having a nice time?
- Yes, thank you.

655
01:06:45,608 --> 01:06:46,276
Kalpana

656
01:06:46,943 --> 01:06:49,237
Did you invite him properly?
- Yes, sir!

657
01:06:50,196 --> 01:06:54,242
If he turns up for real,
everyone'll go mad.

658
01:06:56,286 --> 01:06:57,579
If he doesn't turn up,

659
01:06:58,538 --> 01:06:59,914
then I'll go mad.

660
01:07:02,000 --> 01:07:05,712
Madam...

661
01:07:06,921 --> 01:07:11,676
The coat is ready. Just give me the go
and I'll give you a grand entry.

662
01:07:11,885 --> 01:07:14,220
I've rehearsed it thoroughly.

663
01:07:15,555 --> 01:07:18,433
I'm Sanjay Singhania...
oh hello Sanjay.

664
01:07:20,560 --> 01:07:21,478
Get out of my face.

665
01:07:21,728 --> 01:07:22,854
You fool!

666
01:07:25,732 --> 01:07:27,233
Hi Kalpana...
- Hi!

667
01:07:27,942 --> 01:07:29,069
Mr Singhania has arrived.

668
01:07:45,335 --> 01:07:49,214
Who told him to get a car like that?
I'm not footing this bill.

669
01:07:50,131 --> 01:07:53,301
Oh... thank you.

670
01:07:53,843 --> 01:07:54,678
How wonderful!

671
01:07:55,261 --> 01:08:00,392
He hasn't begun acting and all these fools have
already taken him for Sanjay Singhania?

672
01:08:01,601 --> 01:08:02,769
Oh yes, yes...

673
01:08:03,812 --> 01:08:04,562
Will you hold this, please?

674
01:08:05,605 --> 01:08:06,606
Hi darling!

675
01:08:07,857 --> 01:08:10,193
Sorry, I'm late... my God!
You're looking gorgeous... come.

676
01:08:10,402 --> 01:08:12,946
Welcome to this party.
- Thank you.

677
01:08:14,781 --> 01:08:15,573
Hello... hello...

678
01:08:15,782 --> 01:08:17,117
Hello sir!

679
01:08:17,993 --> 01:08:18,493
Sorry.

680
01:08:18,660 --> 01:08:19,953
Welcome, sir.
- Thank you.

681
01:08:20,161 --> 01:08:24,791
Myself, Satveer Kohli. I'm Kalpana's director
and I run this ad film company.

682
01:08:25,000 --> 01:08:27,627
Hello sir, how are you?
- Thank you sir, I'm very good.

683
01:08:28,169 --> 01:08:31,506
I happen to be the one who insisted that
Kalpana must say yes to you.

684
01:08:32,007 --> 01:08:33,508
I see...?

685
01:08:34,050 --> 01:08:36,761
You never told him!
- Of course I told him...

686
01:08:37,053 --> 01:08:39,431
I told you...?
- Oh... yes...

687
01:08:39,639 --> 01:08:40,807
Autograph, please?

688
01:08:42,309 --> 01:08:46,187
I read your article in Economic Times.
I fully agree with your policy suggestions.

689
01:08:46,354 --> 01:08:49,941
Please leave him alone...
don't disturb him.

690
01:08:50,150 --> 01:08:52,110
Please come, dinner is ready.

691
01:08:59,659 --> 01:09:00,910
That was too close an embrace.

692
01:09:03,038 --> 01:09:05,165
And that was a kiss in public.

693
01:09:07,876 --> 01:09:09,502
I've done a hundred ads.

694
01:09:09,878 --> 01:09:12,422
Ninety in groups. Ten, solo.

695
01:09:12,881 --> 01:09:16,885
You learn how to respect your seniors or,
you're getting nowhere in life.

696
01:09:22,557 --> 01:09:24,017
I don't believe this.

697
01:09:24,934 --> 01:09:25,602
What?

698
01:09:25,894 --> 01:09:27,145
I just can't believe...

699
01:09:27,354 --> 01:09:29,147
Why not...?

700
01:09:29,356 --> 01:09:32,609
Can't believe that I'm sitting
in such august presence...

701
01:09:33,693 --> 01:09:35,445
Still, he's right amongst us.

702
01:09:39,616 --> 01:09:40,325
Excuse me...

703
01:09:44,204 --> 01:09:45,413
Some ice, please?

704
01:09:45,872 --> 01:09:47,415
So much cold is good enough for you.

705
01:09:49,250 --> 01:09:51,836
Over-acting. He'll get caught.

706
01:09:52,128 --> 01:09:53,713
Please get lost.

707
01:09:57,592 --> 01:09:58,551
Excuse me...

708
01:09:59,386 --> 01:10:01,805
We're from the Dinanath Charitable Trust.

709
01:10:02,222 --> 01:10:03,932
It's an orphanage for girls.

710
01:10:04,099 --> 01:10:05,225
And...?

711
01:10:05,433 --> 01:10:07,852
If you may make a contribution,
we'll be grateful.

712
01:10:08,103 --> 01:10:10,522
Who goes around with cash nowadays?

713
01:10:10,730 --> 01:10:12,148
Your cheque will do.

714
01:10:13,608 --> 01:10:14,442
Cheque?

715
01:10:14,985 --> 01:10:17,696
Who goes to parties with chequebooks?

716
01:10:19,948 --> 01:10:22,283
What are you upto?

717
01:10:22,575 --> 01:10:23,702
Whose chequebook is that?

718
01:10:23,994 --> 01:10:25,954
Even for over-acting, this is too loud!

719
01:10:28,790 --> 01:10:31,459
Five hundred thousand?
Have you gone mad?

720
01:10:33,545 --> 01:10:34,921
Thank you, sir.
- All the best.

721
01:10:37,924 --> 01:10:38,675
I'm finished.

722
01:10:42,971 --> 01:10:44,597
I could kill you.

723
01:10:45,223 --> 01:10:46,891
Our leading model, Sonal.

724
01:10:47,100 --> 01:10:48,268
How do you do?
- I'm very good.

725
01:10:48,476 --> 01:10:52,230
Kalpana has told us so much about you...
- We all know that... there're others...

726
01:10:52,439 --> 01:10:56,818
That article of yours in Economic Times.
- Not again, sir. Please...

727
01:11:04,659 --> 01:11:06,995
You... for Sanjay Singhania!

728
01:11:07,162 --> 01:11:08,913
And they fell for you?

729
01:11:12,667 --> 01:11:16,921
Am I'm too clever,
or it's a world of fools?

730
01:11:32,812 --> 01:11:33,563
I love you.

731
01:11:35,148 --> 01:11:35,649
What?

732
01:11:38,735 --> 01:11:42,822
I love you.
I want to marry you.

733
01:11:46,701 --> 01:11:49,371
What... so all of a sudden...?

734
01:11:52,040 --> 01:11:52,999
Not so... all of a sudden.

735
01:11:56,836 --> 01:12:00,048
I never thought...

736
01:12:05,178 --> 01:12:06,554
Give me time, to think.

737
01:12:08,181 --> 01:12:10,141
Shall I tell you tomorrow?

738
01:12:17,190 --> 01:12:19,776
If I say no, you won't take it badly?

739
01:12:32,706 --> 01:12:33,206
Bye.

740
01:12:36,418 --> 01:12:37,335
Happy new year.

741
01:12:38,920 --> 01:12:39,754
Happy new year.

742
01:12:53,518 --> 01:12:55,353
To her, I'm just an ordinary guy.

743
01:12:56,771 --> 01:12:58,023
I wish to remain this unexceptional man...

744
01:12:58,231 --> 01:12:59,607
who wins her love.

745
01:13:02,152 --> 01:13:04,487
So I haven't told her the truth about me.

746
01:13:07,115 --> 01:13:09,034
If she accepts me,

747
01:13:10,910 --> 01:13:13,580
then I'll confess to being Sanjay Singhania.

748
01:13:15,832 --> 01:13:17,375
If she refuses,

749
01:13:19,044 --> 01:13:19,711
then I remain Sachin...

750
01:13:19,919 --> 01:13:23,381
and I fade out of her life.

751
01:13:25,759 --> 01:13:27,469
All I await now, is tomorrow.

752
01:13:38,688 --> 01:13:40,649
End of the diary.
December 31st.

753
01:13:41,483 --> 01:13:45,612
Next day, next year... 2006.

754
01:13:54,537 --> 01:13:56,915
Hey... hey...

755
01:13:57,248 --> 01:13:58,291
The next day, what happened...?

756
01:13:58,583 --> 01:14:00,960
What did she say...
what happened to her?

757
01:14:01,169 --> 01:14:02,671
How did you end up like this?

758
01:14:02,879 --> 01:14:05,423
Speak up!

759
01:16:03,625 --> 01:16:04,376
Hello, sir.

760
01:16:04,959 --> 01:16:05,919
I'm your manager.

761
01:16:06,795 --> 01:16:07,629
Pankaj Shroff.

762
01:16:12,884 --> 01:16:13,760
Hello Sanjay.

763
01:16:13,969 --> 01:16:16,304
I'm your doctor. Dr Peston Wadia.

764
01:16:17,764 --> 01:16:19,265
Not enough sleep.

765
01:16:19,474 --> 01:16:21,810
Are up keeping up till late?

766
01:16:21,977 --> 01:16:25,438
Sir, I'm telling you again,

767
01:16:25,647 --> 01:16:28,608
it's fine if you won't go to the office,
it's okay, no problem.

768
01:16:28,817 --> 01:16:32,862
But live in your mansion,
why this tiny flat?

769
01:16:34,489 --> 01:16:38,076
We can get a nurse, a chauffeur here...?

770
01:16:38,910 --> 01:16:40,328
I need no one.

771
01:16:42,998 --> 01:16:43,790
Thank you.

772
01:16:48,003 --> 01:16:49,838
Kill Ghajini.
Check invitation on Calendar.

773
01:16:52,298 --> 01:16:55,135
Ghajini Dharmatma

774
01:16:58,596 --> 01:17:01,224
Chief Guest: Mr Ghajini Dharmatma

775
01:17:07,480 --> 01:17:11,401
Sir... you're... here...
for our college culture fest?

776
01:17:14,279 --> 01:17:15,780
Oh, I'm sorry.

777
01:17:16,239 --> 01:17:19,576
You won't know me...
I mean, you know me.

778
01:17:19,826 --> 01:17:20,869
I've met you.

