1049
01:50:27,034 --> 01:50:27,785
Three...?

1050
01:50:29,161 --> 01:50:30,579
Can't it climb down by a couple or so?

1051
01:50:31,497 --> 01:50:32,456
No way.

1052
01:50:33,624 --> 01:50:36,502
If you can wait, then wait.

1053
01:50:36,961 --> 01:50:37,711
Otherwise,

1054
01:50:37,920 --> 01:50:39,964
marry a girl of your class.

1055
01:50:42,883 --> 01:50:43,926
I'll wait.

1056
01:50:44,718 --> 01:50:47,805
Don't worry.
Even after I'm rich,

1057
01:50:48,013 --> 01:50:51,433
I'll still be the same to you, like I'm now.

1058
01:50:52,142 --> 01:50:55,104
Promise?
- Promise.

1059
01:51:04,989 --> 01:51:05,990
Good morning, sir.
- Good morning.

1060
01:51:06,156 --> 01:51:07,950
A very happy new year to you.
- Thank you.

1061
01:51:08,409 --> 01:51:09,994
Mr Goenka has canceled for the day.

1062
01:51:10,828 --> 01:51:12,913
The board meeting is at eleven thirty.

1063
01:51:13,581 --> 01:51:15,874
The marketing presentation is post-lunch.

1064
01:51:16,083 --> 01:51:16,625
Okay.

1065
01:51:21,880 --> 01:51:25,843
Sir... what did she say when
she got to know about you?

1066
01:51:28,470 --> 01:51:29,513
I haven't told her.

1067
01:51:31,098 --> 01:51:31,765
Why, sir?

1068
01:51:33,934 --> 01:51:34,894
Because, in 1992...

1069
01:51:35,102 --> 01:51:37,396
her dad had three Ambassador cars.

1070
01:51:37,855 --> 01:51:40,983
Her uncle tricked her dad out of the cars.

1071
01:51:41,901 --> 01:51:44,778
Now she wants to be richer than her uncle.

1072
01:51:45,487 --> 01:51:46,488
Until then, she won't marry.

1073
01:51:46,697 --> 01:51:48,532
What if you just told her...?

1074
01:51:48,699 --> 01:51:51,076
She'd want to be richer than me...

1075
01:51:51,535 --> 01:51:52,828
that'd be the end of my wedding.

1076
01:51:55,164 --> 01:51:59,835
Truth is, I prefer to keep up this facade.

1077
01:52:07,551 --> 01:52:09,303
I had bought this flat...
as my gift to her...

1078
01:52:10,554 --> 01:52:15,184
after telling her about me.
It's not to be,

1079
01:52:16,143 --> 01:52:17,853
but I got to give her the flat, somehow.

1080
01:52:18,562 --> 01:52:19,605
That's your responsibility.

1081
01:52:21,232 --> 01:52:22,107
It'll be done, sir.

1082
01:52:22,900 --> 01:52:23,525
Thanks.

1083
01:52:37,581 --> 01:52:38,832
May no one ever wish you ill.

1084
01:52:39,041 --> 01:52:40,709
And your tank forever be petrol-ful.

1085
01:52:55,099 --> 01:52:57,810
For me too... please.
- Quiet! There's enough for everyone.

1086
01:52:58,018 --> 01:53:00,563
For me, too?
- Late, even today?

1087
01:53:00,771 --> 01:53:02,273
You bought it?

1088
01:53:02,481 --> 01:53:04,191
Yes... surprise.

1089
01:53:04,441 --> 01:53:07,570
One in. Two more to go.
- Great!

1090
01:53:07,945 --> 01:53:10,197
I sold the jewellery meant
for my wedding.

1091
01:53:10,698 --> 01:53:12,199
Dear husband to-be,

1092
01:53:12,408 --> 01:53:13,867
I don't think, you care for a dowry.

1093
01:53:14,076 --> 01:53:15,244
So, I bought a car.

1094
01:53:15,786 --> 01:53:17,705
Sure... it moves?

1095
01:53:18,956 --> 01:53:21,375
Are you joking?
Take a test drive.

1096
01:53:22,793 --> 01:53:23,419
Come on, kids.

1097
01:53:30,885 --> 01:53:32,094
Smooth drive, isn't it?

1098
01:53:32,428 --> 01:53:33,137
Smooth roads.

1099
01:53:33,345 --> 01:53:34,179
Hey...?

1100
01:53:35,764 --> 01:53:37,099
Smooth as butter.

1101
01:53:38,684 --> 01:53:41,312
The radio, there's one in there.
It works!

1102
01:54:01,373 --> 01:54:04,919
Hey, this car is mine!
I just bought it.

1103
01:54:05,127 --> 01:54:09,048
Nice, isn't it?
- What a pretty car!

1104
01:54:30,527 --> 01:54:31,320
Good news, sir.

1105
01:54:31,612 --> 01:54:32,821
The fax is in from London.

1106
01:54:33,030 --> 01:54:34,156
We've got the licence.

1107
01:54:34,365 --> 01:54:36,867
All calls to UK will be routed through us.

1108
01:54:37,034 --> 01:54:38,118
That's wonderful!

1109
01:54:38,369 --> 01:54:39,495
Give the good news to the staff.

1110
01:54:39,703 --> 01:54:41,413
Sure. You must go to
London immediately.

1111
01:54:41,622 --> 01:54:42,289
Yes

1112
01:54:46,835 --> 01:54:47,836
Hi, how are you?

1113
01:54:48,045 --> 01:54:50,422
There's good news!

1114
01:54:50,631 --> 01:54:51,423
Strange!

1115
01:54:51,924 --> 01:54:55,094
She always pips me to the talking post?

1116
01:54:56,679 --> 01:54:57,763
Even I have something to tell you.

1117
01:54:57,972 --> 01:54:59,181
No. Me first.

1118
01:55:01,183 --> 01:55:01,850
Tell me.

1119
01:55:02,142 --> 01:55:05,896
I won a brand new flat in
an Air Voice lucky contest.

1120
01:55:06,897 --> 01:55:09,149
Air Voice lucky contest...?

1121
01:55:10,609 --> 01:55:14,238
Sir... that flat you wanted to give her...
I fixed a contest to do it.

1122
01:55:15,072 --> 01:55:17,074
Wow, that's great! Congratulations.

1123
01:55:17,283 --> 01:55:19,076
Notjust congratulations.

1124
01:55:19,285 --> 01:55:20,911
Get over here in five minutes.

1125
01:55:21,495 --> 01:55:23,872
Kalpana, I'm a bit busy.
I can't come.

1126
01:55:24,081 --> 01:55:26,542
I'll hit you for pretending to be busy.

1127
01:55:27,126 --> 01:55:28,794
I'm giving you the address.
Come right away.

1128
01:55:41,140 --> 01:55:42,016
Hi!

1129
01:55:42,224 --> 01:55:44,393
Hi... congratulations.

1130
01:55:44,602 --> 01:55:45,603
Thank you

1131
01:55:47,271 --> 01:55:48,272
One second!

1132
01:55:52,735 --> 01:55:53,319
What's this?

1133
01:55:57,406 --> 01:55:58,949
You're taking your first step
into this home.

1134
01:55:59,158 --> 01:56:01,702
I want to capture it for posterity.

1135
01:56:05,956 --> 01:56:06,916
You too, come over.

1136
01:57:02,179 --> 01:57:02,972
Nice, isn't it?

1137
01:57:04,181 --> 01:57:04,890
Beautiful.

1138
01:57:05,099 --> 01:57:06,517
This is how it'll stay forever,

1139
01:57:06,684 --> 01:57:09,520
to remind us of the first step we took.

1140
01:57:20,489 --> 01:57:22,658
So! How is this home?

1141
01:57:24,034 --> 01:57:25,035
Fabulous!

1142
01:57:26,036 --> 01:57:28,789
New home, second hand car...

1143
01:57:28,872 --> 01:57:30,207
lucky strike?

1144
01:57:31,083 --> 01:57:32,543
I'm feeling so happy!

1145
01:57:32,876 --> 01:57:34,878
Weren't you saying something
on the phone?

1146
01:57:35,379 --> 01:57:41,343
Yes... I got to go out of town
for ten days.

1147
01:57:42,052 --> 01:57:42,970
Where to...?

1148
01:57:44,388 --> 01:57:45,347
My village.

1149
01:57:47,057 --> 01:57:49,143
Why, so suddenly?

1150
01:57:51,270 --> 01:57:53,022
My mother is sick.

1151
01:57:54,565 --> 01:57:55,983
Then, bring her here.

1152
01:57:56,859 --> 01:57:59,778
I got to go, I have some property there...

1153
01:57:59,987 --> 01:58:01,280
two acres of land.

1154
01:58:01,572 --> 01:58:02,573
I got to sell it...

1155
01:58:02,740 --> 01:58:04,366
for my mother's medical treatment.

1156
01:58:06,493 --> 01:58:11,582
Ten days?
You'll come sooner, if you can...?

1157
01:58:12,458 --> 01:58:13,125
I will.

1158
01:58:14,835 --> 01:58:16,211
You will come, won't you?

1159
01:58:17,338 --> 01:58:18,881
What's it, why are you nervous?

1160
01:58:20,007 --> 01:58:23,636
I don't know, it's just an odd feeling.

1161
01:58:23,844 --> 01:58:24,887
Hey...

1162
01:58:27,890 --> 01:58:29,225
Silly you.

1163
01:58:34,605 --> 01:58:36,148
All the rest are standard clauses.

1164
01:58:36,273 --> 01:58:37,983
I think we've covered everything, right?

1165
01:58:38,192 --> 01:58:40,069
Yes, we've clarified all the points.

1166
01:58:40,945 --> 01:58:44,240
I'll need a hard copy on the flight.

1167
01:58:44,448 --> 01:58:44,949
Will be done.

1168
01:58:45,115 --> 01:58:47,493
Make sure, all changes are incorporated.
- Right.

1169
01:58:47,701 --> 01:58:49,453
Yes...?
- Sir, we're getting late.

1170
01:58:50,537 --> 01:58:53,666
It's one o'clock!
All right, let's pack.

1171
01:58:55,292 --> 01:58:56,460
Thank you, gentlemen.

1172
01:59:02,967 --> 01:59:03,634
Hello?

1173
01:59:03,842 --> 01:59:06,595
Hello Sachin... Kalpana.
- Yes Kalpana?

1174
01:59:06,845 --> 01:59:08,180
I got to see you right away.

1175
01:59:08,973 --> 01:59:10,724
Come over to my old place.

1176
01:59:12,101 --> 01:59:14,853
It's one am. Say, what's the matter?

1177
01:59:15,521 --> 01:59:20,109
I got to see you before you leave.
Please.

1178
01:59:22,152 --> 01:59:23,445
All right. I'm coming.

1179
01:59:37,960 --> 01:59:39,128
Why are you standing on the street?

1180
01:59:39,545 --> 01:59:41,505
Just waiting, for you.

1181
01:59:47,595 --> 01:59:50,222
So... why did you call me?

1182
02:00:00,858 --> 02:00:01,692
What's this?

1183
02:00:02,693 --> 02:00:04,695
One hundred and thirty five thousand.

1184
02:00:05,070 --> 02:00:06,614
For your mother's treatment.

1185
02:00:09,450 --> 02:00:10,659
Where did you get so much money?

1186
02:00:11,744 --> 02:00:12,828
I sold my car.

1187
02:00:13,037 --> 02:00:14,914
What... why?

1188
02:00:16,582 --> 02:00:19,043
You would've sold the land.

1189
02:00:20,044 --> 02:00:22,922
Don't sell it. It's an inheritance.

1190
02:00:23,881 --> 02:00:26,008
A car... I can buy again.

1191
02:00:28,552 --> 02:00:29,178
But...

1192
02:00:31,680 --> 02:00:33,057
you wanted the car so much!

1193
02:00:33,390 --> 02:00:34,016
Forget it.

1194
02:00:34,225 --> 02:00:36,852
Show your mother my soap ad.

1195
02:00:37,102 --> 02:00:38,687
I'm looking nice in that one.

1196
02:00:44,401 --> 02:00:45,653
Come back quickly.

1197
02:00:47,404 --> 02:00:50,199
Next week, I'm in Goa for an ad shoot.

1198
02:00:50,658 --> 02:00:52,034
I'll be back in two or three days.

1199
02:00:52,785 --> 02:00:55,037
You're getting late... now go.

1200
02:01:00,084 --> 02:01:01,210
Go on.

1201
02:01:13,305 --> 02:01:23,274
BIGPictures

1202
02:01:58,559 --> 02:02:03,188
How was it that you came to me

1203
02:02:04,398 --> 02:02:08,193
How blessed I am,
but it's hard to believe

1204
02:02:08,402 --> 02:02:12,197
You descended upon
life's placid lake...

1205
02:02:12,406 --> 02:02:18,120
like a rare Moon,

1206
02:02:18,329 --> 02:02:20,956
slowly,

1207
02:02:21,165 --> 02:02:23,792
gently

1208
02:02:26,837 --> 02:02:30,466
Under a winter's Sun,

1209
02:02:30,674 --> 02:02:33,677
like a warm melody...

1210
02:02:34,094 --> 02:02:36,931
you have caressed me,

1211
02:02:37,139 --> 02:02:45,272
I am enthralled

1212
02:02:45,522 --> 02:02:51,487
In you, my peace.
You are my passion

1213
02:02:51,695 --> 02:02:57,284
Why didn't I find you before?

1214
02:02:57,576 --> 02:03:07,628
How was it that you came to me...
how blessed I am, but it's hard to believe

1215
02:03:09,296 --> 02:03:11,006
That day, I swore...

1216
02:03:11,382 --> 02:03:14,176
until I buy three Ambassador cars,

1217
02:03:14,385 --> 02:03:16,178
I won't marry.

1218
02:03:18,973 --> 02:03:21,809
Don't sell it.
It's an inheritance.

1219
02:03:22,726 --> 02:03:24,979
A car... I can buy again.

1220
02:03:31,235 --> 02:03:37,575
And once I believed,

1221
02:03:38,576 --> 02:03:41,203
that the Creator finds...

1222
02:03:41,412 --> 02:03:43,664
His urge no more

1223
02:03:44,415 --> 02:03:44,915
And then...

1224
02:03:45,082 --> 02:03:50,045
He created you

1225
02:03:50,379 --> 02:03:56,552
And now He is revealed to me...

1226
02:03:56,760 --> 02:04:01,724
in all His glory

1227
02:04:13,277 --> 02:04:17,907
Chords of a music touch my life,

1228
02:04:19,116 --> 02:04:23,078
I can feel new tunes coming into life

1229
02:04:23,287 --> 02:04:33,005
But I still can't believe...

1230
02:04:33,214 --> 02:04:35,633
how blessed I am,

1231
02:04:35,799 --> 02:04:38,594
how you came to me...

1232
02:05:00,574 --> 02:05:01,492
I love you.

1233
02:05:10,960 --> 02:05:12,086
Come back quickly.

1234
02:05:46,245 --> 02:05:49,123
That's upto 21st June 2006.

1235
02:05:49,999 --> 02:05:53,377
Afterwards, Sanjay went to London
and Kalpana went to Goa.

1236
02:05:53,961 --> 02:05:55,170
What happened after that?

1237
02:06:16,150 --> 02:06:20,863
Anything more on the man
we arrested at the girls' hostel?

1238
02:06:21,071 --> 02:06:24,074
No, it's turning out to be a strange case.
- How come?

1239
02:06:26,869 --> 02:06:27,786
Bring him.

1240
02:06:28,329 --> 02:06:32,541
It was tough keeping him under control,
so he was given a sedative.

1241
02:06:37,588 --> 02:06:40,591
He has several names
and numbers tattooed.

1242
02:06:40,758 --> 02:06:43,385
Also, several strange remarks.

1243
02:06:43,844 --> 02:06:44,553
On the head...

1244
02:06:44,887 --> 02:06:46,138
he has a deep scar.

1245
02:06:46,347 --> 02:06:47,056
Found on him...

1246
02:06:47,264 --> 02:06:50,392
a gun, a camera, photographs.

1247
02:06:50,726 --> 02:06:53,771
We haven't been able to
find out who he is.

1248
02:06:56,065 --> 02:06:58,817
Call up those numbers.
Find out who they are.

1249
02:07:15,000 --> 02:07:15,626
Hello?

1250
02:07:16,877 --> 02:07:19,755
Constable Dhuri from
D.N. Nagar Police station.

1251
02:07:37,147 --> 02:07:39,483
Do you recognise this man?

1252
02:07:47,449 --> 02:07:48,158
Yes.

1253
02:07:48,659 --> 02:07:51,203
He is Sanjay Singhania,
chairman of Air Voice.

1254
02:07:51,412 --> 02:07:53,789
The chairman of Air Voice?
- Yes.

1255
02:07:54,748 --> 02:07:56,792
He suffers from short term memory loss,

1256
02:07:57,001 --> 02:08:00,629
doesn't remember anything
beyond 15 minutes.

1257
02:08:01,338 --> 02:08:02,464
A friend of mine,

1258
02:08:03,340 --> 02:08:08,137
he has tattooed in my name and
number, for remembering me.

1259
02:08:10,681 --> 02:08:11,640
That's all.

1260
02:08:12,558 --> 02:08:13,684
Where did you find him?

1261
02:08:14,018 --> 02:08:17,479
Medical college girl's hostel. In a lift.

1262
02:08:17,938 --> 02:08:20,232
Sir, his manager and
his secretary are here.

1263
02:08:20,691 --> 02:08:23,360
Have you written a complaint about him?
- Not yet, sir.

1264
02:08:24,695 --> 02:08:25,654
Wait a while.

1265
02:08:25,946 --> 02:08:27,156
He's only a patient.

1266
02:08:27,907 --> 02:08:29,491
And do you know who he is?

1267
02:08:30,117 --> 02:08:32,244
He was found in a girls' hostel
with a gun.

1268
02:08:32,453 --> 02:08:34,038
How is one to take him
for a medical patient?

1269
02:08:34,246 --> 02:08:36,332
The gun is for his safety.

1270
02:08:37,291 --> 02:08:38,667
Here's the gun licence.

1271
02:08:39,960 --> 02:08:41,670
He didn't shoot at anyone, did he?

1272
02:08:43,422 --> 02:08:45,007
No complaint has been registered.

1273
02:08:45,299 --> 02:08:46,675
You can take him away.

1274
02:08:47,218 --> 02:08:49,511
But from now on, be careful.

1275
02:08:49,887 --> 02:08:52,056
Please take their contact details.

1276
02:08:52,598 --> 02:08:54,350
Thank you.
- Thank you very much.

1277
02:08:54,516 --> 02:08:55,517
Careful.

1278
02:09:33,013 --> 02:09:34,390
Sorry, you aren't allowed...
- Who are you?

1279
02:09:34,598 --> 02:09:36,600
Move over.
- Whom do you want?

1280
02:09:36,809 --> 02:09:37,893
Silence!

1281
02:09:38,102 --> 02:09:39,395
Why are you locking us?

1282
02:09:42,815 --> 02:09:47,444
171, Cheetah Camp. Deonar

1283
02:09:47,987 --> 02:09:50,447
13.06.2008

1284
02:09:51,115 --> 02:09:52,032
Whose address is it?

1285
02:09:52,241 --> 02:09:53,409
Mine.

1286
02:09:54,118 --> 02:09:57,997
The date is tomorrow's.
One day on, you'd be gone.

1287
02:09:59,331 --> 02:10:00,875
Don't shoot him!

1288
02:10:02,501 --> 02:10:06,005
My name and number are on his body.

1289
02:10:06,839 --> 02:10:08,799
In police records,
he's a friend of mine.

1290
02:10:09,383 --> 02:10:13,596
A murder enquiry can
become big trouble.

1291
02:10:13,804 --> 02:10:17,057
You mean, we leave him alive?
- Yes, alive.

1292
02:10:18,392 --> 02:10:19,935
But like the living dead.

1293
02:10:20,644 --> 02:10:23,939
He's got memory tags everywhere.

1294
02:10:24,815 --> 02:10:27,151
We've got to erase what he has written,

1295
02:10:28,485 --> 02:10:31,780
we got to turn him into blank paper.

1296
02:11:40,558 --> 02:11:44,186
Now, he's just like any other furniture

1297
02:11:45,271 --> 02:11:47,314
Just like a vegetable.

1298
02:12:03,205 --> 02:12:05,708
Newspaper archives?
- First floor.

1299
02:13:49,061 --> 02:13:50,688
Why are you hiding?

1300
02:13:51,188 --> 02:13:52,231
Come out.

1301
02:13:53,232 --> 02:13:56,694
Come... careful.

1302
02:13:58,028 --> 02:13:58,821
Sit.

1303
02:14:00,531 --> 02:14:01,574
What happened to you?

1304
02:14:02,283 --> 02:14:04,994
I'm from Latur village.

1305
02:14:05,202 --> 02:14:10,666
Ramesh brought me to Mumbai,
saying he'd find a job for me.

1306
02:14:10,875 --> 02:14:14,753
But he sold me to someone.

1307
02:14:15,880 --> 02:14:21,510
Now... he's forcing me to go to Goa.

1308
02:14:22,052 --> 02:14:26,849
And... there are more girls like me
in a bogey up ahead.

1309
02:14:27,057 --> 02:14:31,896
At one of the stations, I managed to
get away and I'm hiding here.

1310
02:14:32,396 --> 02:14:35,691
Don't cry. Nothing is going to happen.
I'm here with you.

1311
02:14:41,155 --> 02:14:42,031
She must be around.

1312
02:14:42,364 --> 02:14:43,490
Hurry up.

1313
02:14:44,283 --> 02:14:44,867
Move in.

1314
02:14:46,827 --> 02:14:47,536
Look behind.

1315
02:14:53,000 --> 02:14:55,961
Did you see a girl, wearing a frock?

1316
02:14:56,420 --> 02:14:57,504
Give me ten Rupees.

1317
02:14:59,089 --> 02:14:59,882
Here.

1318
02:15:04,261 --> 02:15:08,057
Open the door.
- Open up!

1319
02:15:08,265 --> 02:15:09,475
Give that girl to me!

1320
02:15:10,100 --> 02:15:11,727
I paid 2000 Rupees to buy her!

1321
02:15:11,936 --> 02:15:13,312
Come on, open up!

1322
02:15:13,520 --> 02:15:15,231
Open the door!

1323
02:15:19,443 --> 02:15:21,320
Open it!

1324
02:15:25,699 --> 02:15:26,992
It's gold!

1325
02:15:27,451 --> 02:15:28,619
Should be worth 3,000.

1326
02:15:29,745 --> 02:15:31,539
Forget the girl. Let's go.

1327
02:15:33,791 --> 02:15:34,792
It's all right.

1328
02:15:59,316 --> 02:16:00,276
Don't be afraid.

1329
02:16:00,484 --> 02:16:02,820
We'll get down at the next station
and we'll go to Bombay.

1330
02:16:11,829 --> 02:16:14,248
We've been after chickens.

1331
02:16:14,874 --> 02:16:16,667
Will we spare a hen if we find one?

1332
02:16:20,254 --> 02:16:22,965
Let go... leave her!

1333
02:16:24,717 --> 02:16:26,552
Sister...

1334
02:16:28,679 --> 02:16:31,223
Help me!

1335
02:16:31,432 --> 02:16:31,682
Leave me!

1336
02:16:31,891 --> 02:16:33,350
How far can she run?

1337
02:16:33,684 --> 02:16:36,520
Sister, do something!

1338
02:16:36,729 --> 02:16:38,564
Look at her... there.

1339
02:16:38,772 --> 02:16:43,319
Sister! Help me!

1340
02:17:49,468 --> 02:17:50,970
Hi, how are you?

1341
02:17:51,178 --> 02:17:53,055
I'm okay. Are you in Goa?

1342
02:17:53,430 --> 02:17:55,474
No, I'm returning to Mumbai.

1343
02:17:55,683 --> 02:17:56,350
What?

1344
02:17:56,559 --> 02:17:58,185
It's a long story.

1345
02:17:58,394 --> 02:18:02,231
In my train, there were some goons.
They were taking 25 kidnapped girls to Goa.

1346
02:18:02,815 --> 02:18:04,275
Somehow, I managed to save them.

1347
02:18:04,441 --> 02:18:06,944
I'm on my way back
to Mumbai with them.

1348
02:18:07,278 --> 02:18:09,405
What! Are you all right?

1349
02:18:09,613 --> 02:18:10,906
Tell me about it, what happened?

1350
02:18:11,282 --> 02:18:12,908
Don't worry, nothing's happened to me.

1351
02:18:13,117 --> 02:18:14,076
Are you sure?

1352
02:18:14,285 --> 02:18:17,288
I'm perfectly all right, really.

1353
02:18:17,997 --> 02:18:19,290
You're too much, Kalpana.

1354
02:18:21,625 --> 02:18:24,169
But it's also what I like the
most about you.

1355
02:18:24,628 --> 02:18:25,713
What...?

1356
02:18:25,921 --> 02:18:27,298
This habit of helping others.

1357
02:18:28,007 --> 02:18:29,758
The first time I saw you,

1358
02:18:29,967 --> 02:18:34,555
you were helping some
disabled girls across a ditch.

1359
02:18:35,806 --> 02:18:36,974
How do you know that?

1360
02:18:38,642 --> 02:18:40,853
There's so much I haven't told you.

1361
02:18:41,770 --> 02:18:43,230
Stuff you'll be amazed to hear.

1362
02:18:43,480 --> 02:18:45,608
Drop the melodrama and tell me.

1363
02:18:46,191 --> 02:18:49,236
Not like this...
when I'm saying it,

1364
02:18:49,445 --> 02:18:51,280
I got to see the look on your face.

1365
02:18:52,197 --> 02:18:53,657
So, I'll tell it to you once I'm back.

1366
02:18:53,991 --> 02:18:54,992
See you.

1367
02:18:55,159 --> 02:18:56,201
Take care, bye.

1368
02:18:57,369 --> 02:18:58,245
Bye.

1369
02:19:09,715 --> 02:19:14,803
The biggest news is about kidnapped girls,
trafficking in human organs and flesh trade.

1370
02:19:15,012 --> 02:19:18,390
Last night's revelation has
stunned everyone.

1371
02:19:18,599 --> 02:19:22,978
25 girls from villages in North India lured to
the city on the pretext of giving jobs...

1372
02:19:23,187 --> 02:19:28,776
were being taken from Mumbai to Goa.
With the help of some soldiers,

1373
02:19:29,068 --> 02:19:30,903
Kalpana rescued them.

1374
02:19:31,070 --> 02:19:35,366
Investigations reveal that organs have already
been harvested from these girls.

1375
02:19:35,574 --> 02:19:39,411
Several girls have been operated surgically
and their kidneys have been removed.

1376
02:19:39,620 --> 02:19:44,917
Now they were en route to Goa,
to be pressed into the flesh trade.

1377
02:19:45,251 --> 02:19:48,963
It's apparently a full-fledged racket,
flourishing right across the country.

1378
02:19:49,171 --> 02:19:53,926
Investigations indicate the possible
involvement of influential people.

1379
02:19:54,260 --> 02:19:57,012
Information given by the rescued girls has
led to a country-wide crackdown.

1380
02:19:57,221 --> 02:20:01,225
Several suspects are
being questioned.

1381
02:20:01,433 --> 02:20:07,273
Most of them are women and young girls,
more than half of whom are children.

1382
02:20:18,242 --> 02:20:19,118
Hello

1383
02:20:19,201 --> 02:20:22,872
I'm Constable Vyjayanti.
From Bombay Municipal Hospital.

1384
02:20:23,080 --> 02:20:25,291
Yes, go on.

1385
02:20:25,416 --> 02:20:29,670
Look, you sent 25 girls...?
- Yes?

1386
02:20:29,879 --> 02:20:34,049
Two are missing, without a trace.

1387
02:20:34,592 --> 02:20:36,510
Please come over here
and check them out.

1388
02:20:37,052 --> 02:20:39,722
Please do not mention
that I've tipped you.

1389
02:20:39,930 --> 02:20:42,057
Some very influential people
are behind it.

1390
02:20:57,781 --> 02:20:59,867
Madam... here...?
At this hour?

1391
02:21:00,075 --> 02:21:01,076
Please come in the morning.

1392
02:21:01,285 --> 02:21:03,287
The girls will be let off tomorrow morning.

1393
02:21:03,495 --> 02:21:04,997
I had brought 25 girls.

1394
02:21:05,206 --> 02:21:06,332
There are only 23 here.

1395
02:21:06,540 --> 02:21:08,167
Where are the two girls?

1396
02:21:08,792 --> 02:21:10,336
You are mistaken.

1397
02:21:10,544 --> 02:21:11,795
You brought 23.

1398
02:21:12,004 --> 02:21:13,589
Don't you lie!

1399
02:21:13,714 --> 02:21:16,258
I have a list, of names.

1400
02:21:27,561 --> 02:21:28,479
Good evening, sir.

1401
02:21:32,024 --> 02:21:33,484
Yes.

1402
02:21:33,692 --> 02:21:35,694
You brought in 25 girls.

1403
02:21:36,528 --> 02:21:37,112
Who are you?

1404
02:21:37,321 --> 02:21:38,405
Ghajini.

1405
02:21:38,822 --> 02:21:40,157
Ghajini Dharmatma.

1406
02:21:41,533 --> 02:21:46,789
23 out of 25 named my men.
I'd let it pass.

1407
02:21:47,540 --> 02:21:50,793
But these two, pointed fingers at me.

1408
02:21:52,670 --> 02:21:54,338
Where are the two girls?

1409
02:21:54,588 --> 02:21:57,258
Dead and dumped in the sea.

1410
02:21:59,468 --> 02:22:01,554
Are you asking to know more?

1411
02:22:06,350 --> 02:22:08,269
Because of beasts like you,

1412
02:22:08,477 --> 02:22:10,813
girls are afraid to step out
of their homes.

1413
02:22:15,401 --> 02:22:18,153
Of how many apparitions of men,
should women beware?

1414
02:22:19,405 --> 02:22:21,407
Of keepers of faith and religion?

1415
02:22:22,199 --> 02:22:23,158
Of doctors?

1416
02:22:23,826 --> 02:22:26,871
At work places, in schools, colleges?

1417
02:22:43,095 --> 02:22:43,929
Hello

1418
02:23:04,325 --> 02:23:06,952
Dead and dumped in the sea.

1419
02:23:21,258 --> 02:23:21,759
Hello?

1420
02:23:21,926 --> 02:23:24,970
Vyjayanti speaking...

1421
02:23:25,179 --> 02:23:26,180
Go on.

1422
02:23:26,388 --> 02:23:29,141
They're planning to kill you.

1423
02:23:31,310 --> 02:23:33,229
Please do not go home.

1424
02:23:33,687 --> 02:23:34,897
Go elsewhere.

1425
02:23:35,606 --> 02:23:37,107
They're hiding inside your house.

1426
02:24:12,810 --> 02:24:16,313
What happened?
- A power failure... hold it.

1427
02:24:34,456 --> 02:24:36,917
The door is locked from inside.
She's in here.

1428
02:24:40,337 --> 02:24:41,380
Find her.

1429
02:25:51,242 --> 02:25:52,243
Kalpana...?

1430
02:26:00,584 --> 02:26:01,710
Kalpana

1431
02:26:30,906 --> 02:26:31,865
Kalpana

1432
02:26:47,965 --> 02:26:50,676
Don't go away... don't!

1433
02:27:19,788 --> 02:27:20,414
Fast.

1434
02:27:57,201 --> 02:27:57,785
Hey!

1435
02:27:59,537 --> 02:28:00,329
Look!

1436
02:28:05,376 --> 02:28:06,502
What's it?

1437
02:28:06,877 --> 02:28:08,212
She must've gone that way.

1438
02:28:08,420 --> 02:28:09,296
Go.

1439
02:28:55,009 --> 02:28:55,551
Hello?

1440
02:28:55,759 --> 02:28:57,803
Hello Kalpana... Kalpana...

1441
02:29:32,296 --> 02:29:33,297
Kalpana

1442
02:29:39,136 --> 02:29:40,137
Kalpana

1443
02:29:43,015 --> 02:29:52,983
BIGPictures

1444
02:30:05,663 --> 02:30:06,664
Go away, Sachin.

1445
02:30:09,124 --> 02:30:09,542
Get out.

1446
02:30:09,750 --> 02:30:11,168
Kalpana... what...?

1447
02:30:14,171 --> 02:30:15,381
What happened...?

1448
02:30:21,512 --> 02:30:22,471
Ghajini

1449
02:30:28,185 --> 02:30:29,311
Ghajini

1450
02:30:43,701 --> 02:30:44,702
Kalpana!

1451
02:30:45,202 --> 02:30:46,036
Kalpana...

1452
02:31:40,591 --> 02:31:41,675
Kalpana

1453
02:32:13,582 --> 02:32:15,167
No!

1454
02:33:59,355 --> 02:34:03,525
I'm Sunita. I'm a medical student.

1455
02:35:45,586 --> 02:35:46,712
Forgive me.

1456
02:35:46,921 --> 02:35:48,672
Even I'm responsible for
the state you're in.

1457
02:35:48,881 --> 02:35:50,925
I'll take you to Ghajini.

1458
02:35:51,133 --> 02:35:52,468
I'll bring back your memories.

1459
02:35:52,676 --> 02:35:54,970
I got to talk to him! Now!

1460
02:36:02,019 --> 02:36:04,313
Hello... hello?

1461
02:36:04,521 --> 02:36:06,315
My name is Sanjay.

1462
02:36:06,732 --> 02:36:07,483
What?

1463
02:36:07,900 --> 02:36:09,526
Sanjay Singhania.

1464
02:36:10,569 --> 02:36:12,196
Your name is Ghajini.

1465
02:36:13,822 --> 02:36:16,075
Do you remember the first of July, 2006?

1466
02:36:17,660 --> 02:36:20,829
You may forget, but I cannot forget.

1467
02:36:21,539 --> 02:36:23,082
It's the only thing I remember.

1468
02:36:24,458 --> 02:36:27,044
Leaving you alive was a mistake.

1469
02:36:27,878 --> 02:36:32,341
But now, I'll finish you off.

1470
02:36:32,550 --> 02:36:34,260
This time, no sparing you.

1471
02:36:34,468 --> 02:36:37,429
Wait for your death. I'm coming.

1472
02:36:38,681 --> 02:36:40,182
Damn you!

1473
02:36:42,017 --> 02:36:47,731
Damn... a short-term memory-loss
patient is reminding me?

1474
02:36:50,943 --> 02:36:54,405
Get the cars.
We're going into my den.

1475
02:36:54,905 --> 02:36:56,532
Let him come to my area.

1476
02:36:58,200 --> 02:37:00,536
After I'm through,

1477
02:37:01,245 --> 02:37:03,455
they won't find even a fingernail on him.

1478
02:37:18,637 --> 02:37:19,889
They're going somewhere.

1479
02:37:20,389 --> 02:37:21,348
Follow them.

1480
02:38:01,555 --> 02:38:02,890
They're stopping here.

1481
02:38:03,098 --> 02:38:04,516
Which one is Ghajini?

1482
02:38:05,851 --> 02:38:07,311
The man in white.

1483
02:38:19,823 --> 02:38:21,617
This looks like a dangerous area.

1484
02:38:21,825 --> 02:38:23,661
I think we shouldn't wait here.

1485
02:38:28,123 --> 02:38:29,542
Where are you going?

1486
02:38:29,542 --> 02:38:30,626
You can't kill him so easily.

1487
02:38:30,834 --> 02:38:32,086
There are too many of them in there.

1488
02:38:32,294 --> 02:38:34,129
Stop! We'll get him when he's alone.

1489
02:38:34,338 --> 02:38:35,464
This is a very dangerous area.

1490
02:38:35,673 --> 02:38:37,049
Have you gone mad?

1491
02:38:41,011 --> 02:38:41,804
Oh God!

1492
02:38:58,195 --> 02:39:07,204
Hey stop... Where are you going?
Entry is barred

1493
02:39:55,878 --> 02:39:57,504
He's here! Tell the boss.

1494
02:40:12,144 --> 02:40:13,187
He's coming!

1495
02:40:14,271 --> 02:40:15,231
Move it...

1496
02:40:15,439 --> 02:40:16,815
let's get him!

1497
02:40:17,024 --> 02:40:19,360
Don't let him get away!
- Get the irons...

1498
02:40:19,568 --> 02:40:20,986
He won't get away!
- Don't let him in.

1499
02:41:56,165 --> 02:41:57,666
Boss...

1500
02:42:18,479 --> 02:42:22,983
Now you're gone... finished!

1501
02:48:13,250 --> 02:48:14,043
Brother...

1502
02:48:14,585 --> 02:48:17,087
help me... save me!

1503
02:48:17,421 --> 02:48:19,590
Ghajini is coming... that way!

1504
02:48:19,798 --> 02:48:20,841
Please, help me!

1505
02:48:21,425 --> 02:48:22,551
I'm Prakash!

1506
02:48:22,760 --> 02:48:23,594
Have you forgotten?

1507
02:48:23,761 --> 02:48:25,095
We came for Ghajini!

1508
02:48:25,304 --> 02:48:26,555
Look at how badly he has bruised me!

1509
02:48:26,764 --> 02:48:29,808
I'm Prakash...
Ghajini did this to me.

1510
02:48:31,101 --> 02:48:32,102
He hit me so badly.

1511
02:48:32,269 --> 02:48:34,063
He's a very dangerous man!

1512
02:48:34,939 --> 02:48:36,482
Very dangerous!

1513
02:48:36,732 --> 02:48:37,942
He's coming that way.

1514
02:48:38,609 --> 02:48:40,027
Keep an eye out for him.

1515
02:48:40,986 --> 02:48:42,154
Keep an eye on him.

1516
02:48:42,738 --> 02:48:43,447
Watch out

1517
02:48:44,281 --> 02:48:47,910
Cunning man... very cunning man.

1518
02:48:54,291 --> 02:48:55,918
Got you!

1519
02:49:19,441 --> 02:49:20,609
Got you!

1520
02:49:21,151 --> 02:49:23,404
Short term memory loss...

1521
02:49:24,822 --> 02:49:26,991
Look at my face.

1522
02:49:27,825 --> 02:49:29,076
Look.

1523
02:49:29,159 --> 02:49:30,953
I am Ghajini.

1524
02:49:31,328 --> 02:49:32,288
I am.

1525
02:49:32,830 --> 02:49:35,624
I am the one you wanted to kill.

1526
02:49:35,833 --> 02:49:36,959
Do you remember why?

1527
02:49:44,091 --> 02:49:46,468
Your memory is too weak,

1528
02:49:47,219 --> 02:49:49,305
lasts you forjust 15 minutes.

1529
02:49:50,097 --> 02:49:51,140
But have no regrets.

1530
02:49:53,058 --> 02:50:00,441
In these final 15 minutes of your life,
I'll give the action replay, over again.

1531
02:50:11,785 --> 02:50:13,204
Remember the rod...?

1532
02:50:14,622 --> 02:50:17,208
The one that I used to kill your fiancee?

1533
02:50:19,210 --> 02:50:20,419
Somewhat like this one...

1534
02:50:21,962 --> 02:50:23,172
it comes to your mind?

1535
02:50:29,053 --> 02:50:32,431
I killed her right in front of your eyes.

1536
02:50:39,521 --> 02:50:41,690
Before I kill you,

1537
02:50:41,899 --> 02:50:47,238
I'll show you exactly
how I killed your Kalpana.

1538
02:50:49,073 --> 02:50:49,949
Watch this.

1539
02:55:13,337 --> 02:55:15,047
Kalpana Home for Orphans

1540
02:55:41,323 --> 02:55:44,577
Let's go cut the cake.
- Yes... let's all go.

1541
02:55:48,622 --> 02:55:50,666
Time to cut your cake.

1542
02:55:52,293 --> 02:55:54,086
Wait!

1543
02:55:55,170 --> 02:55:57,506
Sanjay, what's her name?

1544
02:56:00,217 --> 02:56:01,385
Rahul... no.

1545
02:56:07,141 --> 02:56:08,017
Pooja.

1546
02:56:10,060 --> 02:56:11,437
You read it here!

1547
02:56:11,645 --> 02:56:13,606
Cheater... cheater...

1548
02:56:13,814 --> 02:56:26,035
Happy birthday to you.

1549
02:57:55,708 --> 02:58:05,676
BIGPictures

1550
02:58:10,639 --> 02:58:13,267
Pathways, streams and rivers all change

1551
02:58:13,475 --> 02:58:16,145
Glimmering lamps cast lights of change

1552
02:58:16,353 --> 02:58:19,148
When the change strikes life's rhythm

1553
02:58:19,356 --> 02:58:22,109
The rhythm of the rain will also change

1554
02:58:22,318 --> 02:58:27,656
And the nature of seasons will change

1555
02:58:28,240 --> 02:58:32,161
But I shall forever be...

1556
02:58:32,369 --> 02:58:36,165
the same to you as I've been

1557
02:58:36,373 --> 02:58:41,962
Arm in arm, with you my mate,

1558
02:58:42,171 --> 02:58:44,840
every moment,

1559
02:58:45,049 --> 02:58:47,092
always

1560
02:59:03,400 --> 02:59:07,863
How was it that you came to me

1561
02:59:09,240 --> 02:59:12,993
How blessed I was,
but it's hard to believe

1562
02:59:13,202 --> 02:59:16,997
You descended upon
life's placid lake...

1563
02:59:17,206 --> 02:59:22,878
like a rare Moon,

1564
02:59:23,087 --> 02:59:25,756
slowly,

1565
02:59:25,965 --> 02:59:28,217
gently

1566
02:59:31,679 --> 02:59:35,140
Under winter's Suns,

1567
02:59:35,349 --> 02:59:38,185
like a warm melody...

1568
02:59:38,769 --> 02:59:44,400
you caressed me, now you're gone

1569
02:59:44,775 --> 02:59:50,072
But I still live, enthralled

1570
02:59:50,531 --> 02:59:56,245
In you, my peace.
You are my passion

1571
02:59:56,453 --> 03:00:01,917
Why didn't I find you before?

1572
03:00:01,959 --> 03:00:12,553
How was it that you came to me...
how blessed I was, but it's hard to believe

1573
03:02:08,252 --> 03:02:14,550
And once I believed,

1574
03:02:15,634 --> 03:02:20,556
that the Creator finds
His urge no more

1575
03:02:21,390 --> 03:02:26,687
And then He created you...

1576
03:02:27,354 --> 03:02:32,902
